## TileKey.parent() method

Returns a tile key representing the parent of the tile addressed by this tile key.

Throws an exception is this tile is already the root.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
parent(): TileKey;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

[TileKey](./harp-geoutils.tilekey.md)
